text: Markus Glueck (born 15 February 1990) is an Austrian bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Austria Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
